full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/21/2023 A TAT CA MOI NGUOI TI NAN TU 17 TUOI TRO LEN NHAP CANH VAO HOA KY DUOC , COI NHU LA NGUOI VO QUOC TICH (PAROLE) PHAI NAP TO BAO DAM VA CHIUTRACH- NHIEM VE TAI SAN CUA MINH. Toi, THiEu BANH xin the va khai rang: 1. Toi hien CO ky thac trong cac Ngan Han tai Hoa Ky va cac quoc gia khac mQt so tien nhu sau: Dia Diem Ten Ngan Hang So Tien 2. Toi hien CO so tien ky quy tai Hoa Ky va cac nuoc khac tinh theo gia thi truong nhu sau: Cong ty/Co quan chanh phu So kho phan hoac tien ky quy Tri gia 3. Toi hien la so huu chu cua so bat dong san tai Hoa Ky va tai cac quoc gia khac nhu sau: Dia diem Tri gia Tinh ca nguon loi khai thac 4. Toi hien CO mot so ngoai tÃª, vang, bac, kim cuong, cac vat khac CO gia tri, va cac do My thuat tai Hoa Ky va cac quoc gia khac Dia diem Tai Vat Tri gia 5. Toi la SO huu chu so tai vat bat dong san va tai vat ca nhah tai Hoa Ky va tai cac quoc gia khac, chua duoc liet ke tren day: Dia diem Tai vat Tri gia 6. Tong so tai vat tri gia nhu sau: Ky ten day du va chinh thuc cua duong don Duong don voi ten tren day da duoc tuyen the tai ngay (thang/ngay/nam Ten thong dich vien (viet bang chu in) Chu ky cua thong dich vien Chu ky va cap bac cua si quan) (Neu can, hay them nhung yeu to can thiet noi mat sau cua to khai nay) Mau G-648 (6-2-75) Bo Tu Phap Hoa Ky So Ngoai Kieu va Nhap Tich Vietnamese
